<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>HairFlow AI Plans</title>

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial;
background:#f9f9f9;
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
}

h1{
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.plans{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:30px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.plan{
background:white;
padding:30px;
width:280px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.plan h2{
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.plan p{
line-height:1.6;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:20px;
padding:12px 25px;
background:black;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:5px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Choose Your Plan</h1>

<div class="plans">

<div class="plan">
<h2>Basic</h2>

<p>
Automatically sends reminder texts and follow-up messages to customers after they book an appointment.
</p>

<a href="checkout.html?plan=basic" class="button">
Choose Plan
</a>

</div>

<div class="plan">

<h2>Premium</h2>

<p>
Fully automates calls so customers can make appointments over the phone without you doing a thing.
</p>

<a href="checkout.html?plan=premium" class="button">
Choose Plan
</a>

</div>

<div class="plan">

<h2>Diamond</h2>

<p>
Automates calls and texts so customers can book appointments automatically while also sending reminders and follow-up messages.
</p>

<a href="checkout.html?plan=diamond" class="button">
Choose Plan
</a>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
